- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category as the paper deals with identifying and distinguishing between legitimate and malicious accounts on Twitter. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the development of a model for bot detection. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper uses machine learning techniques for classification.
